      "name": "Battery Electric Vehicle (BEV) Manufacturers and Battery Management Systems",
      "description": "Manufacturers and system integrators focusing on battery thermal management, battery state monitoring, and safety in electric vehicles using pressure sensors to monitor battery pack conditions and detect thermal events.",
      "evidence_text": "Pressure sensors in the battery pack provide valuable information of working pressures and unusual pressure increases as input for the Battery Management System. The pressure signature of a thermal event occurs faster than the local temperature increase, pressure sensors can accurately detect thermal events within sealed lithium ion battery cell earlier than temperature sensors alone.",
